01:00:58.490 --> 01:01:00.610
&gt;&gt; John Cole: Could you repeat
the question once for us?

01:01:00.610 --> 01:01:02.980
&gt;&gt; How did it feel when
you wrote your first book?

01:01:02.980 --> 01:01:07.540
&gt;&gt; John Cole: How did you feel
when you wrote your first book?

01:01:07.540 --> 01:01:08.840
&gt;&gt; Kate DiCamillo:
