01:01:16.930 --> 01:01:21.720
I had written a book just because
I had been asked to write a book

01:01:21.720 --> 01:01:26.230
by the church, but my first
novel, I had gone for seven years

01:01:26.230 --> 01:01:32.780 position:56%
