short story and the magazine folded,

01:01:32.780 --> 01:01:40.540
but I decided if I could
write a story a week,

01:01:40.540 --> 01:01:44.690 position:56%
none of which were selling, I could
even write a chapter a week and even

01:01:44.690 --> 01:01:46.800
if nobody ever bought
it or published it,

01:01:46.800 --> 01:01:50.150
I would have accomplished
something by the end of the year.

01:01:50.150 --> 01:01:53.800
So, I set myself the task
of writing a chapter a week.

01:01:53.800 --> 01:01:59.870
